snippet.textDisplay: I fucking subbed! I always loved Gordon but I hardly sub to anything. Not gonna make a big rant. But this means so much to me that I had to sub. Not only is it the most unexpected crossover, but it's so nice to see just how down to earth Ramsay is with being cool with having Steve-O over. I grew up on CKY prank videos, Jackass and Viva La Bam and doing crazy shit myself with skater culture. It's nice to see respect for an odd art that most people don't understand or just dismiss. RIP Don Vito and Ryan Dunn. And thank You Gordon, this made my day during a depressing and shitty time with this Covid-19. :'D
